HEADWORD: Hoggish
<hw>Hog"gish</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Swinish; gluttonous;
filthy; selfish.</def> -- <wordforms><wf>Hog"gish*ly</wf>,
<pos>adv.</pos> -- <wf>Hog"gish*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Is not a <qex>hoggish</qex> life the height of some men's
wishes?</q> <rj><qau>Shaftesbury.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Hogh</ent>⟦br⟧
